<br>
Yes, I'm serious.  I *suspect* that chain aggro is related to the method of attack, and maybe the level of hate.  My beastlord can shuriken pull things single where pulling with drowsy wakens others.<br>
<br>
I recently heard of people singling using sneak+shuriken, but haven't had much chance to explore this.<br>
<br>
I took both my beastlord and my mage through the loda kai camp in shadeweavers, both solo.  Beastlord could single pull using shuriken.  Mage could not.  With knives, mage pulled doubles.  With nukes, she got even more.  Level did not seem to be relevant in this case.<br>
<br>
I will try pulling with cancel very soon, (and with several other classes as well).  It wouldn't surprise me much if cancel had a low &quot;splash&quot; aggro radius.<br>
<br>
Aanni - mage24<br>
Auji - beastlady33<br>
